title: Bridgehead Coffeehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A coffeehouse that offers organic coffee and organic soy milk and some food. Vegan versions of most beverages possible. Prepared foods include baked goods, salads, sandwiches, and the soup is usually vegan. Staff is knowledgeable about veganism and have ingredient lists handy.
